Banco BTG Pactual May Buy Stake in Traffic Sports, Veja Reports

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-04-09T16:20:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/banco-btg-pactual-may-buy-stake-in-traffic-sports-veja-reports.html
Banco BTG Pactual SA, the Brazilian
investment bank led by billionaire  Andre Esteves , may buy a
stake in Brazilian sports marketing agency Traffic Sports,  Veja 
magazine said in its Radar column, without saying where it got
the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in  Sao Paulo  at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at   dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 